text: Tician Tushi (born 2 April 2001) is a Swiss professional footballer who plays as a forward for FC Basel in the Swiss Super League. ==Club career== Tushi made his professional debut with Basel in a 2-1 Swiss Super League win over FC Thun on 22 May 2019. ==International career== Tushi was born in Switzerland and is of Kosovan Albanian descent.
